<noinclude>
This is the "Metaphor" template.  While the name is Metaphor, it is used to display members of the VettedMetaphor category.
It should be called in the following format:
<pre>
{{Metaphor
|Name gloss=
|Name transcription=
|Aliases={{Metaphor.Alias}}
|Description=
|Metaphor Level=
|Metaphor Type=
|Experiential basis=
|Source frame=
|Target frame=
|Mappings={{Mapping}}
|Related metaphors={{Related metaphor}}
|Entailments={{Entailment}}
|Examples={{Example}}
}}
</pre>
Edit the page to see the template text.
</noinclude><includeonly>{| class="wikitable"
|- {{#if:{{{Name gloss|}}}| |style="display:none;"}}
! Name Gloss
| {{Printgloss|{{PAGENAME}}|{{{Name gloss|}}}}}{{#set:Metaphor.Name gloss={{{Name gloss|}}}}}
|- {{#if:{{{Name transcription|}}}| |style="display:none;"}}
! Name Transcription
| [[Metaphor.Name transcription::{{{Name transcription|}}}]]
|-
! Aliases
| {{{Aliases}}}
|-
! Description
| [[Has description::{{{Description|}}}]]
|-
! Metaphor Level
| [[Metaphor.Level::{{{Metaphor Level|}}}]]
|-
! Metaphor Type
| {{#arraymap:{{{Metaphor Type|}}}|,|x|[[Metaphor.Type::x]]}}
|-
! Experiential Basis
| [[Metaphor.Experiential basis::{{{Experiential basis|}}}]]
|}
{| class="wikitable"
! Source Frame
| [[Metaphor.Source frame::Frame:{{{Source frame|}}}|{{{Source frame|}}}]]{{#set:Has source frame=Frame:{{{Source frame|}}}}}{{#ifeq:{{{Source frame|}}}|||{{#info:'''Roles:'''{{#ask: [[Frame:{{{Source frame|}}}]]  [[Role::+]]
| ?Role= | +index=1
| mainlabel=-
| heading=none}}}}}}
|-
! Target Frame
| [[Metaphor.Target frame::Frame:{{{Target frame|}}}|{{{Target frame|}}}]]{{#set:Has target frame=Frame:{{{Target frame|}}}}}{{#ifeq:{{{Target frame|}}}|||{{#info:'''Roles:'''{{#ask: [[Frame:{{{Target frame|}}}]]  [[Role::+]]
| ?Role= | +index=1
| mainlabel=-
| heading=none}}}}}}
|}
{{#set:Metaphor.Investigated for={{{Investigated for|}}}}}

